query:
INSERT INTO installation_steps (inspection_item_id, step_name, step_order, is_completed, completed_quantity)
SELECT 
  ii.id,
  step.name,
  step.order_num,
  0,
  0
FROM inspection_items ii
CROSS JOIN (
  SELECT 'Instalação' COLLATE utf8mb4_unicode_ci as name, 1 as order_num
  UNION ALL SELECT 'Acabamento' COLLATE utf8mb4_unicode_ci, 2
  UNION ALL SELECT 'Finalizado' COLLATE utf8mb4_unicode_ci, 3
) step
WHERE NOT EXISTS (
  SELECT 1 FROM installation_steps ist 
  WHERE ist.inspection_item_id = ii.id 
  AND ist.step_name COLLATE utf8mb4_unicode_ci = step.name COLLATE utf8mb4_unicode_ci
);
